createRegressors

public static double[] createRegressors(double abscissa,
                                        int degree)
This method is to be used for linear regression of a curve. It creates the regressors that can be used in the Ordinary Least Square method

Parameters:
abscissa - The abscissa where the regressors have to be calculated
degree - The maximum degree of the regression
Returns:
An array of regressors of the given degree, for the given value of abscissa
